1178
00:50:39,456 --> 00:50:40,544
(Message received)

1179
00:50:41,024 --> 00:50:43,233
(Passing it along as is)

1180
00:50:43,233 --> 00:50:44,992
(Most understood it properly)

1181
00:50:44,992 --> 00:50:45,792
DANIEL: Stay calm.

1182
00:50:46,366 --> 00:50:47,466
(But occasionally)

1183
00:50:47,800 --> 00:50:49,833
(Some are off-frequency)

1184
