1188
00:51:43,488 --> 00:51:44,096
TRAINEE: Hello.

1189
00:51:44,096 --> 00:51:45,012
TRAINEE: Hello.

1190
00:51:45,012 --> 00:51:47,552
TRAINEES: Hello.

1191
00:51:47,552 --> 00:51:51,000
