1192
00:51:54,300 --> 00:51:56,233
SONGHA: Thank you so much to everyone

1193
00:51:56,233 --> 00:51:58,533
SONGHA: who joined us for the WOOJEONG HIGH festival.

1194
00:51:58,944 --> 00:52:00,192
SONGHA: First of all...

1195
00:52:00,192 --> 00:52:01,760
