1196
00:52:03,168 --> 00:52:07,666
SONGHA: First of all, even though we're still trainees,

1197
00:52:07,966 --> 00:52:11,266
SONGHA: we want to thank everyone

1198
00:52:11,266 --> 00:52:14,166
(Expressing gratitude to all who helped)
SONGHA: who gave us this opportunity.

1199
00:52:14,266 --> 00:52:15,072
HANBI: Thank you.

1200
00:52:15,072 --> 00:52:15,600
TRAINEE: Thank you.

1201
00:52:15,600 --> 00:52:16,416
KASSHO: Thank you.

1202
00:52:16,766 --> 00:52:17,920
TRAINEE: Thank you.

1203
00:52:18,400 --> 00:52:21,566
HANBI: And since we're trainees,

1204
00:52:21,866 --> 00:52:23,666
HANBI: opportunities to meet you directly

