1209
00:52:32,288 --> 00:52:34,528
(Made this performance even more special)
HANBI: the stage together

1210
00:52:34,528 --> 00:52:35,616
HANBI: face to face like this.

1211
00:52:36,333 --> 00:52:37,280
DANIEL: That's right.

1212
00:52:37,280 --> 00:52:38,016
HANBI: Here.

1213
00:52:38,266 --> 00:52:40,900
(To those who came to Busan and those who couldn't)
HANBI: Whether you were able to come or not,

1214
00:52:40,928 --> 00:52:43,633
HANBI: we're truly grateful to all the fans

1215
00:52:43,633 --> 00:52:46,624
HANBI: who always love, support, and stand by us.

1216
00:52:46,624 --> 00:52:47,136
HANBI: Thank you.

1217
00:52:47,136 --> 00:52:49,728
TRAINEES: Thank you.

1218
00:52:50,144 --> 00:52:51,600
SONGHA: And although

1219
00:52:51,600 --> 00:52:53,700
SONGHA: we don't know

1220
00:52:53,700 --> 00:52:56,000
SONGHA: what will happen to each of us,

1221
00:52:56,192 --> 00:52:57,312
SONGHA: we all share

1222
00:52:57,952 --> 00:52:59,008
SONGHA: the same

1223
00:52:59,712 --> 00:53:02,944
SONGHA: dream to debut.

1224
00:53:04,096 --> 00:53:06,400
SONGHA: Please keep supporting us

1225
00:53:06,400 --> 00:53:07,744
SONGHA: until the end.

1226
00:53:08,160 --> 00:53:10,048
HANBI: Even as time passes and seasons change,

1227
00:53:10,048 --> 00:53:12,608
HANBI: thank you sincerely for waiting,

1228
00:53:12,608 --> 00:53:15,904
HANBI: supporting, and responding to us.

1229
00:53:16,352 --> 00:53:17,120
SONGHA: Thank you.

1230
00:53:17,280 --> 00:53:20,100
(No matter how many times they say it, it's not enough)
TRAINEES: Thank you!

1231
00:53:20,224 --> 00:53:22,048
