NICHOLAS: SONGHA, please do a cheek heart!

1242
00:53:34,784 --> 00:53:35,584
(A great moment to watch)
NICHOLAS: With HANBI.

1243
00:53:35,584 --> 00:53:36,416
HARUTA: Show us.

1244
00:53:36,992 --> 00:53:37,696
SONGHA: With HANBI?

1245
00:53:37,696 --> 00:53:38,304
HANBI: Okay, let's go.

1246
00:53:38,304 --> 00:53:39,360
TRAINEE: Together, together.

1247
00:53:39,360 --> 00:53:40,736
TRAINEES: One, two, three.

1248
00:53:41,000 --> 00:53:43,600
(Cheek heart to celebrate HANBI's birthday)
TRAINEES: HANBI, happy birthday!

1249
00:53:43,833 --> 00:53:46,240
(Birthdays are celebrated for two days, apparently)

1250
00:53:46,240 --> 00:53:47,264
- TRAINEE: Happy birthday!
- SONGHA: Thank you.

1251
00:53:48,366 --> 00:53:51,400
(Time to end the festival now!)
SONGHA: Please everyone, head home safely,

1252
00:53:51,584 --> 00:53:54,233
(And don't forget the most important vote!)
SONGHA: and don't forget to vote on your way out!

1253
00:53:54,233 --> 00:53:55,600
DANIEL: WONHA~JANNI! Let's go!

1254
00:53:55,600 --> 00:53:57,120
(And just like lighting a fuse...)

1255
00:53:57,933 --> 00:53:58,944
