1256
00:53:58,944 --> 00:53:59,968
TATA: Five Boys Over Flowers.

1257
00:54:01,133 --> 00:54:01,733
HANBI: Be quiet!

1258
00:54:01,866 --> 00:54:02,966
HANBI: Please be quiet!

1259
00:54:03,072 --> 00:54:03,392
TRAINEE: Okay.

1260
00:54:03,392 --> 00:54:04,096
TRAINEE: I'm sorry.

1261
00:54:04,096 --> 00:54:04,866
(Chaos contained)

1262
00:54:04,966 --> 00:54:06,300
