HANBI: we've been SMTR.

1264
00:54:07,900 --> 00:54:08,704
HANBI: Everyone.

1265
00:54:08,704 --> 00:54:10,592
TRAINEES: Thank you.

1266
00:54:10,592 --> 00:54:11,584
