1268
00:54:13,088 --> 00:54:14,816
TRAINEE: TATA, TATA.

1269
00:54:14,816 --> 00:54:15,584
TRAINEE: Were you late?

1270
00:54:16,468 --> 00:54:17,536
TRAINEE: TATA, why are you late?

1271
00:54:17,536 --> 00:54:18,400
(The 15-member synchronized bow
isn't going to match until the end)

1272
00:54:18,400 --> 00:54:19,136
TRAINEE: Thank you.

1273
00:54:19,296 --> 00:54:20,480
TRAINEE: Get home safely.

1274
00:54:20,480 --> 00:54:21,504
(To all the fans who joined the festival)
TRAINEE: Take care not to catch a cold.

1275
00:54:21,504 --> 00:54:22,880
(Sincerely thank you to all fans)
TRAINEE: Please get home safely.

1276
00:54:22,880 --> 00:54:23,552
TRAINEE: Thank you.

1277
00:54:23,552 --> 00:54:24,416
TRAINEE: Thank you.

1278
00:54:24,416 --> 00:54:25,100
TRAINEES: Thank you.

1279
00:54:25,100 --> 00:54:26,112
