HYUNJUN: Please vote for A.U.I!

1280
00:54:26,112 --> 00:54:26,848
TRAINEE: A.U.I.

1281
00:54:26,848 --> 00:54:27,392
TRAINEE: Thank you.

1282
00:54:27,392 --> 00:54:28,224
