1287
00:54:32,160 --> 00:54:32,832
TRAINEE: The best!

1288
00:54:35,392 --> 00:54:36,833
DANIEL: This is the most fun!

1289
00:54:37,120 --> 00:54:38,528
DANIEL: Wow, this is the most fun.

1290
00:54:39,124 --> 00:54:39,808
