1311
00:55:47,666 --> 00:55:48,300
HAMIN: Good job!

1312
00:55:48,300 --> 00:55:49,568
HANBI: Everyone did a great job.

1313
00:55:50,048 --> 00:55:50,688
KACHIN: Good job.

1314
00:55:51,166 --> 00:55:55,200
TEACHERS' OFFICE: Our WOOJEONG HIGH SCHOOL's life
