1343
00:56:50,272 --> 00:56:51,584
NICHOLAS: We don't know yet.

1344
00:56:51,584 --> 00:56:52,160
WOOLIN: Let's go!

1345
00:56:53,066 --> 00:56:54,166
TEACHERS' OFFICE: How about it, everyone?

1346
00:56:54,166 --> 00:56:55,266
TEACHERS' OFFICE: Do you have a feeling who will win?

1347
