1353
00:57:02,240 --> 00:57:04,133
TRAINEES: Five Boys Over Flowers!

1354
00:57:04,133 --> 00:57:04,640
NICHOLAS: A.U.I!

1355
00:57:04,640 --> 00:57:06,752
