1364
00:57:17,733 --> 00:57:18,533
TEACHERS' OFFICE: Now that you've met

1365
00:57:18,533 --> 00:57:22,033
TEACHERS' OFFICE: the fans
who came to support you today,

1366
00:57:22,033 --> 00:57:24,533
