1471
01:00:38,500 --> 01:00:40,133
TEACHERS' OFFICE: I hope the memories you made here

1472
01:00:40,133 --> 01:00:43,966
TEACHERS' OFFICE: become
the driving force for your future.

1473
01:00:43,966 --> 01:00:45,504
