younger members like these)

1569
01:03:30,496 --> 01:03:32,864
SONGHA: Well, if you call me boomer, I guess I am.

1570
01:03:33,366 --> 01:03:35,666
SONGHA: But everyone has grown so much until now...

1571
01:03:35,666 --> 01:03:38,533
SONGHA: We made it here because we had

1572
01:03:38,533 --> 01:03:40,544
