KASSHO: Are you crying?

1581
01:04:00,608 --> 01:04:01,536
JUSTIN: I'm not crying!

1582
01:04:01,632 --> 01:04:03,680
JUSTIN: No, you're usually the one who cries.

1583
01:04:03,808 --> 01:04:05,900
JUSTIN: Don't interrupt me.

1584
01:04:06,166 --> 01:04:06,976
