1585
01:04:06,976 --> 01:04:07,776
JUSTIN: It's okay, it's okay.

1586
01:04:08,033 --> 01:04:10,300
HANBI: How these 15 people here will debut,

1587
01:04:10,300 --> 01:04:12,100
HANBI: and what paths we will take, we don't know,

1588
01:04:12,416 --> 01:04:13,504
HANBI: but we will always

1589
01:04:13,504 --> 01:04:16,233
HANBI: be fellow teammates.

1590
01:04:16,640 --> 01:04:18,080
