01:04:24,096 --> 01:04:25,024
SADAHARU: Ah, seriously.

1595
01:04:25,024 --> 01:04:26,144
SADAHARU: I don't wanna wake up.

1596
01:04:26,144 --> 01:04:27,360
SONGHA: Yeah, I don't want to wake up.

1597
01:04:28,166 --> 01:04:29,568
TATA: I was happy just now.

1598
01:04:29,568 --> 01:04:30,304
TATA: Later...

1599
