1605
01:04:43,552 --> 01:04:44,480
SONGHA: Good work everyone, thank you.

1606
01:04:44,480 --> 01:04:45,312
TRAINEES: Thank you.

1607
01:04:45,312 --> 01:04:47,040
HANBI: One, two, three.

1608
01:04:47,648 --> 01:04:48,480
